          <h3>üì∫ Streaming Service</h3>
          <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Netflix stream buffering in India</p>
          <p><strong>Traditional Solution:</strong> Replicate all content to India data center (~2000ms away from Virginia)</p>
          <p><strong>Edge Solution:</strong> Cache popular content at edge in Mumbai, Bangalore, Delhi (~50ms away)</p>
