          <p><strong>Traditional Solution:</strong> Send sensor data to cloud, wait for response (500ms+ latency)</p>
          <p><strong>Edge Solution:</strong> Process on-device and at nearby edge nodes (~50ms total latency)</p>
          <p class="result">Result: Safe driving, edge handles camera analysis and path planning</p>
        </div>

        <div class="example">
          <h3>üè• Remote Diagnostics</h3>
