          <p><strong>Traditional Solution:</strong> Send all data to cloud, process centrally</p>
          <p><strong>Edge Solution:</strong> Local edge analyzes instantly, sends only anomalies to cloud</p>
          <p class="result">Result: Real-time monitoring, 99% less data transmission</p>
        </div>

        <div class="example">
          <h3>üéÆ Gaming</h3>
