      <div class="challenges-grid">
        <div class="challenge">
          <h3>üîÄ Consistency</h3>
          <p>Data distributed across 300+ locations means keeping it consistent is hard.</p>
          <p class="solution">Solution: Use eventual consistency, CRDTs, or synchronize with central database</p>
